{"tid":231033,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"如果你知道我係邊個，你一定唔夠膽串我","createTime":"2017-05-05T18:12:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-05T20:28:54.000Z","uid":86038,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"26b79504e9bd03647ffeea596f030d25e13faf28","tid":231033,"uid":86038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T18:12:11.000Z","msg":"夜幕低垂，涼風靜靜吹過。<br />\n<br />\n一罐可樂、一個蛋撻，口腔嘗出的甜味剛好反映我輕快的心情。<br />\n<br />\n儘管天空沒有星，那怕身旁沒有人。<br />\n<br />\n我腦海仍然播放着美妙的音樂自娛自樂。<br />\n<br />\n巴哈，小步舞曲。<br />\n<br />\n坐在天台上，眼前的維港景色化為演奏團，舞動雙手，輕輕指揮着大家。<br />\n<br />\n輕快的拍子令我不斷哼唱起來，忘我的在天台間表演，卻忘記了正事。<br />\n<br />\n我將身旁的染滿血的麻布袋用力推下街道，然後繼續我的個人表演。<br />\n<br />\n果然&hellip;&hellip;蛋撻還是酥皮比較好。"},{"pid":"98045bba1395a0bdd2e985293fcb17db47410b19","tid":231033,"uid":86038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T18:36:06.000Z","msg":"人之將死，其言善也。<br />\n<br />\n只是從恐懼之中安慰自己既行為，善？<br />\n<br />\n渴求死前或者死後會有一個好結局迎接自己。<br />\n<br />\n虛偽、偽善。<br />\n<br />\n侮改如果唔係由內疚開始形成，而係由恐懼開始。<br />\n<br />\n依樣就唔再係悔改，係乞憐。<br />\n<br />\n當我用刀仔逐吋逐吋鋸果位牧師做人肉刺生果時，佢充分證咗人係往往從利益開始考慮。"},{"pid":"e344b7e46cfc82a2bec8a65b5d9ba53e4d6a9c2b","tid":231033,"uid":100347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T18:45:13.000Z","msg":"竟然無圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"100e83b55259be5cc5cc19ca222cc2860db44081","tid":231033,"uid":106081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T18:45:55.000Z","msg":"刺生果...<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f849a8ca65dc272f95371d7f4f296c17b549d2f6","tid":231033,"uid":32179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T18:55:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette2.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/7/7c/E29c0f03f57a26d7cfe8d920722d23ce.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20070703200119\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette2.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F7%2F7c%2FE29c0f03f57a26d7cfe8d920722d23ce.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20070703200119&h=71e6f4cb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"57ee9dbabd62b0f9d0e3f178c3e0b357df4ba3b5","tid":231033,"uid":86038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T18:57:33.000Z","msg":"「我無興趣。」<br />\n<br />\n「不相信主的羔羊必定會落地獄！」牧師指着我說道。<br />\n<br />\n「荒謬，一個殺人犯殺人無數只要懺悔信主就可以上天堂？」<br />\n<br />\n「只要弟兄願意接受主的教誨，主會寬恕 你。」牧師在我面前畫着十字架的手勢。<br />\n<br />\n「只要信主，就會寬恕我？」<br />\n<br />\n「無錯，請返回正途吧。」牧師按着手上的聖經說道。<br />\n<br />\n「我有啲懷疑，可唔可以證明俾我睇？」<br />\n<br />\n「無問題，你想點證明？」<br />\n<br />\n哈。"},{"pid":"7625b1cac0a3c9aa268148c2bae2910ea66863f0","tid":231033,"uid":86038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T18:58:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>竟然無圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你串我？"},{"pid":"5c8f2c25cb3af78628f07197d01623480b7385e6","tid":231033,"uid":86038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T19:13:41.000Z","msg":"「救命&hellip;&hellip;救命呀！」被牢牢縛緊的牧師大叫着。<br />\n<br />\n咒我落地獄？醒你一個左勾拳。<br />\n<br />\n「點呀牧師，將你縛成耶穌一樣開唔開心呀？嘿嘿！」<br />\n<br />\n「你個痴線佬！上帝唔會放過你！」牧師震抖着聲線說道。<br />\n<br />\n「依家又唔放過我，你個神都幾鬼馬喎。」<br />\n<br />\n「既然我都唔放過，咁你呢！」我拿起手上的照片放在牧師面前。"},{"pid":"ec6f3db54cabd5d63ffd88454441dc7498aad939","tid":231033,"uid":86038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T19:34:22.000Z","msg":"「大快活主任曹美女？」牧師看着相片說道。<br />\n<br />\n屌，攞錯。"},{"pid":"8d044b7918d086dc7257b4387f574c9b67ea87dd","tid":231033,"uid":86038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T20:10:07.000Z","msg":"「嘿嘿&hellip;&hellip;」牧師忍不住笑聲。<br />\n<br />\n「笑我！」我憤怒的大吼。<br />\n<br />\n我拿着小刀利落的刺穿牧師的腦袋，腦漿猶如噴泉般濺出。<br />\n哈哈哈！哈哈哈！哈哈哈！<br />\n<br />\nLIHKG: <br />\n<br />\n                   <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">冷血殺人狂</div></strong></span><br />\n#7 <span style=\"color: blue;\">易經丁</span>「垃圾文收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n#8 <span style=\"color: blue;\">故台評分員</span> 「文章鬆散凌亂，欠缺故事主題 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">F-</span></span>」<br />\n<br />\n#9 <span style=\"color: red;\">絲絲思詩詩</span> 「咪住先，明明又話逐吋逐吋鋸，依家又一刀拮爆頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n#10 <span style=\"color: blue;\">力威掙扎</span>「樓主收皮啦，翻屋企打飛機啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n#11 <span style=\"color: blue;\">嘴炮專員</span> 「如果垃圾文係一種侵略武器，相信閣下可以稱霸全宇宙」<br />\n<br />\n#12 <span style=\"color: red;\">曹美女</span> 「垃圾樓主好心咪亂用我個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n#13 <span style=\"color: red;\">西水長流</span> 「出現了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當我獨自一人看着電腦螢幕時，心裏一鼓怒氣爆發出來，大力的一拳打向電腦並大聲叫道&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果你知道我係邊個，你一定唔夠膽串我！</span></span>"},{"pid":"4c8e6567293aa2615d3ac774a302cad937f2bdfc","tid":231033,"uid":86038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T20:28:54.000Z","msg":"我叫曹民禮，今年十六歲，我想成為一個小說作家。<br />\n<br />\n不過睇怕&hellip;&hellip;算啦都係放棄。<br />\n<br />\n毒撚最忌有自信。<br />\n<br />\n即刻開新ac先，廢時俾人起底。<br />\n<br />\n叫咩名好呢？啊！一於叫「東山再起」<br />\n<br />\n<strong>**「帳戶名稱已被使用」**</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你，恰鳩我！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"}]}